data.value:
--v0.8-- [+] Fixed the Save/Load Function ( Finally ! ) [-] Reduced the PvP No Delay to reduce DC
--v0.7-- [+] Added PvP No Delay ( Select a key from the comboBox and hold it to enable it in PvP )
--v0.6-- [+] Added CC dc prevention [+] Added Aran Skill Key Bind [+] Added a Mins/Sec comboBox for you to choose in the timed CC section
--v0.5-- [+] Added Exploits & Auto CC [+] Added a Map image downloader ( currently not working though :\ ) [+] Fixed the Heavy CPU Usage :D [+] Fixed Skill Bug
--v0.4-- [+] Change the Main Form's GUI :D [+] Added MorphHack and Anti MorphHack <9's the Id for godmode> [+] Added No Breath , still just FYI , this doesn't bypass the breath check .
--v0.3-- [+] Added a splashscreen as i saw this leeched into another hacking site w/o my permission [+] Fixed the AutoLoot / AutoSkill Problem [+] Added Auto Refresh Map (delay/attack), this actually resets your time in those mini dungeons :) [-] Removed WallVac as it a/b's TOO easily
--v0.2-- [+] Added Wallvac . To activate it , tick wallvac and enter CS then Exit CS , the mobs should be stuck on the coordinates you entered . Be careful though , wallvac a/b's easily if you don't CC/CS frequently [+] Added iEatSteroids and Always Face Left (CS) [+] Fixed Exp Pointer
